content.html: I just finished #TheExpanse. It was an excellent series. 10/10. Each and every actor did a stellar job. It had beautiful lessons on love, friendship, loss, & leadership. I am sad to leave these characters. They were beautiful.
content.value:

content.html: If you enjoyed the show, consider the #expanse books. I genuinely believe @JamesSACorey wrote the finest literature to come out in my lifetime. It’s a truly epic tale about the human tendency to destroy ourselves.
